{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"07jw7rf43we9fv2oldtor3r","title":"Reference-Counted","desc":"","updated":1669145133099,"created":1669144019066,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.Smart-Pointer.Reference-Counted","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"c8d6f8b521e256763f4004f780ba556b","links":[],"anchors":{"reference-counted-smart-pointer-rct":{"type":"header","text":"Reference Counted Smart Pointer Rc<T>","value":"reference-counted-smart-pointer-rct","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"share-data":{"type":"header","text":"Share data","value":"share-data","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"cloning-an-rct-increases-the-reference-count":{"type":"header","text":"Cloning an Rc<T> increases the Reference Count","value":"cloning-an-rct-increases-the-reference-count","line":34,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"xpd7irdmeinvljufhfbgq6a","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"reference-counted\">Reference-Counted<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#reference-counted\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"reference-counted-smart-pointer-rct\">Reference Counted Smart Pointer <code>Rc&#x3C;T></code><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#reference-counted-smart-pointer-rct\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>There are cases when a single value might have <strong>multiple owners</strong>.</li>\n<li>The <code>Rc&#x3C;T></code> keeps track of the <strong>number of references</strong> -> if the value is still on use</li>\n<li>The <code>Rc&#x3C;T></code> is only use for <strong>single-threaded</strong> scenarios.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"share-data\">Share data<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#share-data\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token keyword\">enum</span> <span class=\"token type-definition class-name\">List</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">i32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">List</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">Nil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">crate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token class-name\">List</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Nil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">std<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span>rc<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Nil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">clone</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// increasing the number of references (1 -> 2)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">clone</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// increasing the number of references (2 -> 3)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code>Rc::clone</code> doesn't make a deep copy of all the data like the <code>clone</code>\n<ul>\n<li>Save time &#x26; space</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cloning-an-rct-increases-the-reference-count\">Cloning an <code>Rc&#x3C;T></code> increases the Reference Count<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#cloning-an-rct-increases-the-reference-count\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">new</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Nil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// inital = 1</span>\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">println!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"count after creating a = {}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">strong_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// count after creating a = 1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">clone</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">println!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"count after creating b = {}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">strong_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// count after creating b = 2</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Cons</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">clone</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token macro property\">println!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"count after creating c = {}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">strong_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// count after creating c = 3</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// c goes out of scope here</span>\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">println!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"count after c goes out of scope = {}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">strong_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// count after c goes out of scope = 2</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</cod